items.headline: Welcome to the Khumba Wiki
items.desc: The movie, Khumba, is about a half-stripes zebra who makes a long distance journey to gain his stripes. Khumba is an outcasted zebra who is determined to gain his stripes. He meets some pretyy eccentric friends and a couple enemies along his journey. From a zebra clan in an enclosed gate to a legendary hero in all of South Africa.
